<br>
The planes as they used to exist are gone.  They used to be the ultimate challenge for a group of 30 or so level 50's.  There were only 3 such challenges available, and a large population of 46-50 who wanted to do them, so the calendar was created.  2 more continents have been added since then, and a lot of new challenges, but there are obviously a great deal of people who still consider this encounter the end-all be-all of the game, and refuse to give an inch.<br>
<br>
