<br>
For most classes, the armor that drops in Fear/Hate is 6th or 7th on the list of the best armor they can get.  This is the pre-Kunark equivalent of fighting over spawns that drop bronze.<br>
<br>
My favorites are the people who call the uberguilds greedy.  GREEDY! LOL!  They want to get in there to fight a ubermob and try to develop tactics to take him down with a very large chance that they will fail completely.  This is the absolute core of what the game is about.  The people screaming about this are going in with their copy of &quot;How to break fear&quot; that was written in 1999 taped to the side of their computer to farm armor for their friends.  Who exactly is the greedy one here?<br>
<br>
